## Contacts [/contacts/]

Contacts are the people or businesses who buy products or services from you.  They're identified by a unique `id`.


### Create a Contact [POST /contacts]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
    
            Authorization: Bearer <API_KEY>
        
